+++++ Special Containment Procedures:
SCP-x045 is almost impossible to enter, and is believed to be completely impossible to exit. The only known way to influence one's chances to enter SCP-x045 is through the use of [DATA EXPUNGED], which is kept in secure containment in Site 814.

+++++ Description: 
SCP-x045 is a pocket dimension that manifested at the central point of [DATA EXPUNGED].

SCP-x045-1 is [DATA EXPUNGED].

SCP-x045-2 is an anomalous Digital Television (DTV) signal that originates from within SCP-x045. The signal broadcasts what appears to be an early 2000's American sitcom titled "Welcome to Wanderson," that features a rotating cast of bizarre and strange characters.

SCP-x045-3 is an anomalous phenomenon known as "segmentation"[[footnote]]9M9H9E9[[/footnote]]. Segmentation is a method of cutting in which the fabric of space time itself is separated, rather than the physical matter of the object being segmented. This has two results: It allows objects to be cut into pieces, without interfering with the objects function, and it allows for the creation of non-Euclidean zones in standard reality. The matter removed during the process of segmentation is transported into SCP-x045, seemingly via teleportation.
